42:59.844 --> 43:03.014 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SHAKA SENGHOR: So, 90 percent of
who are incarcerated
will at some point get out.

43:03.047 --> 43:07.752 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we have to decide what kind
