44:13.618 --> 44:17.889 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think sometimes you can
tell the deeper
truths through fiction, because
it is not

44:17.922 --> 44:23.628 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
