personal. Sometimes,
it gives you enough distance to
really kind

44:23.661 --> 44:25.530 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
of think about things
differently.

44:25.563 --> 44:30.868 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so literature played a
