48:58.102 --> 49:02.239 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I wonder if any of them are
prepared to make
a real personal sacrifice for
the good of

49:02.273 --> 49:08.946 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
this nation. And yet such acts
