49:37.174 --> 49:42.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
People like Mr. Bauman are the
true heroes
of this country. This Fourth of
July, think

49:42.746 --> 49:48.285 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about the people, young and old,
rich and
poor, citizen and non-citizen,
who have made

49:48.319 --> 49:50.387 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
