49:50.421 --> 49:56.527 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Some are in uniform, but many
are not. They
all deserve our respect, but,
more than that,

49:56.560 --> 50:01.665 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
